Code: 

package pattern;

public class SquareHallow {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		int r = 4;
		int c = 4;
		for(int i=0;i<4;i++) {
			for(int j=0;j<4;j++) {
				if(i==0 || i==r-1 || j==0 || j==c-1) 
					System.out.print("*");				
				else
					System.out.print(" ");
		}
			System.out.println(" ");

	}

}
}


Output:

**** 
*  * 
*  * 
**** 

